Definition: a gambling card game of Spanish origin
Example: 3 or 4 cards are dealt face up and players bet that one of them will be matched before the others as the cards are dealt from the pack one at a time
Synonyms: four-card_monte, three-card_monte, card_game, a, gambling, card, game, of, Spanish, origin, or, cards, are, dealt, face, up, and, players, bet, that, one, them, will, be, matched, before, the, others, as, from, pack, at, time
Category: noun.act
